{"tid":369842,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友一唔開心 點氹都無用 比著你會點做","createTime":"2017-08-22T15:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T19:21:51.000Z","uid":73202,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc1e41fbcf5b3a763e80b2eca01df481f8fb933a","tid":369842,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"佢話過 <br />\n通常 佢過一段時間就無事 <br />\n佢啲朋友都係咁同我講 <br />\n話佢一向都係咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每次氹佢 都只會令情況惡化<br />\n最後佢會怪自己點解咁煩 <br />\n<br />\n比著你 會繼續氹 定等佢過一段時間搵返你(24小時內)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次我選擇咗等佢好翻啲先再傾"},{"pid":"c6ae29d517c22641f11db8a1ee628fd639939e75","tid":369842,"uid":137908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T15:40:45.000Z","msg":"唔好理 等佢搵你"},{"pid":"b2514714c41d3730caf68bd1e3419b27fc364cf0","tid":369842,"uid":115946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"同佢講 嬲完就揾翻你啦"},{"pid":"b2c7bfe1823945a32a9f93b1e9ad2538dbda024d","tid":369842,"uid":5806,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"係面前嘅攬住佢 再氹再攬都冇用就飛咗佢啦"},{"pid":"20eed437bf171435a75323c82fd58ba075927e24","tid":369842,"uid":56791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"佢嬲你果段時間 去陪二奶先"},{"pid":"d6f205366f64ef3ca79df42d87719620dc38dbb6","tid":369842,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"搵過個男朋友代替，又唔駛氹又易溝通"},{"pid":"5bc0afbb6ebf6090a69a142ef0515f02b0e3f4aa","tid":369842,"uid":139238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T15:52:50.000Z","msg":"佢本身學業/事業上有壓力？"},{"pid":"9e6fcb4c0cfab0b3f0c217668012a8b987064887","tid":369842,"uid":64343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:04:22.000Z","msg":"人地啲fd都話係咁<br />\n你氹都無用 每人傷心時既處理方法都唔同"},{"pid":"0acab537c87c6804dfdc5